{"tid":1481444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有冇人飲清酒.....了解下","createTime":"2019-08-17T17:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T04:42:35.000Z","uid":10434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3ac9ad4b3074c7ed7a3f33caefa3ca98af8a1bc0","tid":1481444,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"連登臥虎藏龍，威士忌有，紅酒有，清酒有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最好的時代要飲酒，依家仍然要，香港加油....8.18見大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470098463a5e03469fb0c6524bab2416652dd82a","tid":1481444,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"14代大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff5aa0858b588f6b29ce1f5035cb2db41fb6311","tid":1481444,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743f0d6096e146de83967d4627ad89811d9ded0d","tid":1481444,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470098463a5e03469fb0c6524bab2416652dd82a","tid":1481444,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"14代大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，未試過14代，可唔可以分享下感受"},{"pid":"b91cd465fa951b38cf47651fae6ad251755fb0a7","tid":1481444,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff5aa0858b588f6b29ce1f5035cb2db41fb6311","tid":1481444,"uid":97776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:44.000Z","msg":"lm學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:14:35.000Z","msg":"唔敢當唔敢當，大家分享下<br />\n小弟覺得威士忌層次同味道較鮮明，紅酒其次，清酒則屬於一切較細緻的，仍在吸取知識階段....<br />\n<br />\n之前試過用水不同，味道亦可以差好遠，好有趣"},{"pid":"15fce960440a80c92e79975b9b69dd69910b6360","tid":1481444,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"743f0d6096e146de83967d4627ad89811d9ded0d","tid":1481444,"uid":10434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470098463a5e03469fb0c6524bab2416652dd82a","tid":1481444,"uid":141419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"14代大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:11:33.000Z","msg":"小弟不才，未試過14代，可唔可以分享下感受"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"我味覺唔係好靈，同時都詞窮，成日形容唔到好貼切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好話不才！太謙啦！<br />\n個種入口好清新好純嘅口感唔識點形容，非常非常非常易入喉，就好似做完運動好口渴飲杯冰水嘅狀態，入完喉少少少少少刺激喉嚨嘅感覺，再係鼻噴番股氣出嚟，成個鼻都聞到股好香嘅味！（米？）<br />\n都係痴酒飲到多<br />\n試過七垂十二貫，白雲去來，龍泉<br />\n但對上一次飲到都係34月事，話個陣感覺仲好記得係呃人（我自己記憶問題）<br />\n不過聽講好似keep唔耐同成日再放雪櫃"},{"pid":"8cdef3def256bf36f1b9e45f6a221679d15bcf0f","tid":1481444,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:27:40.000Z","msg":"器由路？"},